column5: Driving by the area and noticed trees were clear cut at riverbank? Does anyone know why? BTW, the river is still frozen.
Won't be frozen for long.  I'm guessing they are widening that road so people stop launching themselves into the river and drowning.
I just pumped a bridge deck on the 6th line and west of 10 th sdrd. I know they have rehabbed a bunch of bridges in the area already and have more to do.
